[src:generating-functions-deep/umbral-calculus] A similar relationship holds for the backward differences and rising factorial.
[src:generating-functions-deep/umbral-calculus] This series is also known as the *Newton series* or **Newton's forward difference expansion**.
[src:generating-functions-deep/umbral-calculus] The analogy to Taylor's expansion is utilized in the calculus of finite differences.
